<paragraph base="F16150085" id="IAS19_25" principles="no"><paranum>25</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 19"/><data name="paranum" value="25"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS19_P0159">Although this Standard does not require specific disclosures about <xref base="F16148489" href="IAS19_0001.dita#IAS19_0001/IAS19_UN0002">short&#x2011;term employee benefits<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0353"/></ph></xref>, other IFRSs may require disclosures. For example, <xref base="F16223421" href="../ias24/IAS24_TOC0001.dita#IAS24_TOC0001" id="IAS19_X0245">IAS 24</xref>              requires disclosures about <xref base="F16148487" href="IAS19_0001.dita#IAS19_0001/IAS19_UN0001">employee benefits<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0098"/></ph></xref> for key management personnel. <xref base="F16223452" href="../ias01/IAS01_TOC.dita#IAS01_TOC0001" id="IAS19_X0247">IAS 1 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Presentation of Financial Statements</ph></ph></xref>              requires disclosure of employee benefits <xref base="SL138596" href="IAS19_1.dita" scope="local">expense<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_expenses"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>